Summary: Outside something caught my eye. It was the outline of an ET
divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside and something caught my eye. I walked over and in the cement that is what I saw. I went in and took some pictures with a digital camera outside it was dark by then. It was unbelievable the number of varied shapes and forms coming through the cement. The next day I continued taking pictures a short time later it started to drizzle and I took a couple of pictures. Today is the 10th of Oct. I feel everything happens for a reason, I shared these photos with over a dozen people they saw what I saw and more. One of my friends told me about this site. When looking or talking about the photos I get a tingle.
